 the advisory board of kingsett capital qualifications with  years of experience leading a global financial institution and one of canadas largest public companies mr nixon brings extensive expertise and perspective to the board on global markets and an indepth knowledge of the north american market his experience growing a diversified global financial services organization in a highly regulated environment also provides the board with valuable insight into risk management compensation and corporate governance matters source blackrock inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view gordon m nixons full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like gordon m nixon more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in gordon m nixons network and community follow changes in gordon m nixons employment and moneyinmotion connect with gordon m nixon through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example gordon m nixon gordon m nixons connections  sign up now to view gordon m nixons  connections » sarabjit s marwah former vice chairman and chief operating officer the bank of nova scotia ronald a brenneman former president and chief executive officer petrocanada willard galen g weston former executive chairman george weston limited paul r weiss former board member bce inc robert l goldstein senior managing director and chief operating officer blackrock inc robert e brown former president and chief executive officer cae inc stephen howe former executive vice president and chief technology officer bce inc robert w fairbairn senior managing director blackrock inc john s lacey former board member loblaw companies limited j richard kushel senior managing director and global head multiasset strategies group blackrock inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita ev